dct_title_s: Map of Colorado Territory, and northern portion of New Mexico : showing the system of parcs
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Shows drainage, settlements, county boundaries, transportation lines, township lines, etc. From: Gilpin, William. Mission of the North American people, geographical, social and political. Philadelphia : J.B. Lippincott & Co., 1874.
